<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>The Cozy Nook</h1>
        </div>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/shop">Shop</a></li>

                <% if (typeof user !== 'undefined' && user.firstname) { %>
                    <li><a href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
                    <li>Hello, <%= user.firstname %></li>
                <% } else { %>
                    <li><a href="/login">Account</a></li>
                <% } %>

                <li><a href="/cart">Cart</a></li>
                <li><a href="/wishlist">Wish List</a></li>
                <li><a href="/api-tester">API Tester</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- Search Bar -->
        <form action="/search" method="GET" class="search-form">
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
                <!-- Dropdown for category selection -->
                <select name="category" required>
                    <option value="books">Books</option>
                    <option value="authors">Authors</option>
                    <option value="publishers">Publishers</option>
                </select>
        
                <!-- Input field for the search query -->
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    name="query" 
                    placeholder="Search..." 
                    required 
                    style="width: 200px; padding: 8px;"
                />
        
                <!-- Search button -->
                <button type="submit" style="padding: 8px 16px;">Search</button>
            </div>
        </form>
        
        
    </header>

    <% if (typeof welcome !== 'undefined') { %>
        <div class="welcome-banner">
            Welcome, <%= welcome %>! <a href="/login">Log in</a> to make a purchase.
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <main>
        <div class="welcome-section">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>This is an online bookstore that allows users to search for books, place orders, and manage their accounts.</p>
            <p>Welcome to The Cozy Nook — your curated online destination for exceptional books across a range of captivating genres.</p>
            <p>We are an independent online bookstore, founded from a desire to offer readers a more bespoke and meaningful book-buying experience.</p>
            <p>At The Cozy Nook, we believe books are more than products — they are stories that shape us, knowledge that empowers us, and escapes that comfort us.</p>
            <br/>
            <p>Our mission is to provide limited edition, handpicked, and thoughtfully categorized books for readers </p>
            <p>who appreciate quality and uniqueness. Whether you’re a casual browser, a seasoned bibliophile, or </p>
            <p>someone searching for a thoughtful gift, we’ve crafted our collections to meet your literary needs.</p>
            <p> We specialize in the following categories from Science Fiction, Romance, Thrillers, Fantasy, and Mathematics.</p>
            <br/>
            <p>We aim to combine the charm of a small neighborhood bookstore with the reach and convenience of </p>
            <p>modern web technology. Each book you find here has been selected not only for its content but for its ability to inspire.</p>
            <br/>
            <p>Thank you for being part of our journey. We hope you enjoy every page you turn at The Cozy Nook.</p>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 The Cozy Nook. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
